stories.title: Sunny's last opus
stories.subTitle: Classic World Cup Moments
stories.seoTitle: Classic World Cup Moments: Sunil Gavaskar's last opus, 1987
stories.summary: Gavaskar was a different batsman in 1987, having shed some of his orthodoxy, and against New Zealand, he played the sort of innings few expected from him

stories.title: India's hat-trick hero
stories.subTitle: Top Performances
stories.seoTitle: Top World Cup Performances: Chetan Sharma comes the first bowler to take a World Cup hat-trick
stories.summary: Chetan Sharma was known for producing the odd peach. Here he trotted out three in a row

videos.title: Gavaskar's last opus
videos.summary: Sunil Gavaskar hit his only ODI century - an uncharacteristically quickfire one - to help India easily overhaul New Zealand's small total
